Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.03,0:00:18.38,Default,,0,0,0,,原諒我
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.78,0:00:22.37,Default,,0,0,0,,我無法拯救你
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.64,0:00:38.29,Default,,0,0,0,,大哥哥 又睡不著嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.94,0:00:39.89,Default,,0,0,0,,鬼神…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.15,0:00:41.06,Default,,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.28,0:00:43.60,Default,,0,0,0,,不好好睡覺腦子會壞掉的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.34,0:00:46.52,Default,,0,0,0,,大哥哥 等等
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.74,0:00:47.65,Default,,0,0,0,,等我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.85,0:00:50.11,Default,,0,0,0,,大哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.76,0:00:57.36,Default,,0,0,0,,還是搞不懂啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.56,0:00:59.74,Default,,0,0,0,,明明收拾掉了那個妖狐
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.85,0:01:01.88,Default,,0,0,0,,身體還是沒有復原
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.99,0:01:04.49,Default,,0,0,0,,尋找 斬殺 直到復原為止
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.84,0:01:06.61,Default,,0,0,0,,話雖如此
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.60,0:01:08.63,Default,,0,0,0,,但是大哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.07,0:01:11.00,Default,,0,0,0,,自從離開醍醐你太逞強了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.28,0:01:15.13,Default,,0,0,0,,不好好休息光顧著斬妖除魔
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.71,0:01:17.57,Default,,0,0,0,,這樣下去身體吃不消…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.42,0:01:19.46,Default,,0,0,0,,好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.04,0:01:24.42,Default,,0,0,0,,現在威脅國家安危的哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.64,0:01:26.28,Default,,0,0,0,,才是鬼神！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.80,0:01:31.85,Default,,0,0,0,,我無法拯救你
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.80,0:01:34.77,Default,,0,0,0,,大哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.67,0:01:38.98,Default,,0,0,0,,雖說沒了爸爸媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.58,0:01:40.57,Default,,0,0,0,,也要好好活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.06,0:01:45.24,Default,,0,0,0,,我會陪著大哥哥的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.54,0:01:46.51,Default,,0,0,0,,大哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.99,0:03:21.05,Default,,0,0,0,,白面不動之卷
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.03,0:03:25.22,Default,,0,0,0,,在哪裡？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.32,0:03:27.09,Default,,0,0,0,,在那座山對面
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.26,0:03:28.28,Default,,0,0,0,,謝啦 大叔
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.11,0:03:31.40,Default,,0,0,0,,大哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.36,0:03:33.95,Default,,0,0,0,,有溫泉喔
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.29,0:03:35.25,Default,,0,0,0,,知道嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.37,0:03:37.62,Default,,0,0,0,,山上會自己湧出熱水喔
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.28,0:03:40.80,Default,,0,0,0,,去那裡的話大哥哥也能好好休息了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.23,0:03:43.12,Default,,0,0,0,,媽媽說溫泉不僅能讓身體放鬆
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.12,0:03:45.12,Default,,0,0,0,,還能讓心情平靜下來
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.07,0:03:49.78,Default,,0,0,0,,總之我們走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.36,0:03:57.34,Default,,0,0,0,,傳言那溫泉附近有妖怪出沒
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.62,0:04:08.17,Default,,0,0,0,,朝倉軍隊已退
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.00,0:04:11.24,Default,,0,0,0,,又降恩惠之雨
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.81,0:04:37.89,Default,,0,0,0,,現在還不能解除和鬼神的契約
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.94,0:04:41.64,Default,,0,0,0,,但這樣下去
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.21,0:04:43.06,Default,,0,0,0,,總有一天…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.71,0:04:56.92,Default,,0,0,0,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.63,0:04:58.33,Default,,0,0,0,,放開我
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.76,0:05:00.21,Default,,0,0,0,,你不是我老婆吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.33,0:05:01.49,Default,,0,0,0,,放開我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.47,0:05:04.12,Default,,0,0,0,,放手
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.21,0:05:08.46,Default,,0,0,0,,你要幹什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.75,0:05:49.60,Default,,0,0,0,,果然這張臉也不對
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.88,0:06:06.34,Default,,0,0,0,,在這過夜再合適不過了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.67,0:06:08.44,Default,,0,0,0,,大哥哥就好好休息吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.89,0:06:11.18,Default,,0,0,0,,我去找點木柴和果子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.22,0:06:15.12,Default,,0,0,0,,還有 這裡說不定是強盜的據點
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.12,0:06:16.16,Default,,0,0,0,,要小心喔
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.39,0:06:17.79,Default,,0,0,0,,但是不能殺掉他們
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.89,0:06:20.05,Default,,0,0,0,,教訓一下就行了喔
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.26,0:06:28.41,Default,,0,0,0,,撿了很多了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.54,0:06:33.66,Default,,0,0,0,,瀑布的聲音？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.93,0:06:44.27,Default,,0,0,0,,好厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.05,0:06:56.45,Default,,0,0,0,,什麼？好大的佛像…別嚇我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.84,0:06:57.55,Default,,0,0,0,,小孩
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.27,0:07:02.63,Default,,0,0,0,,我很難吃的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.05,0:07:04.82,Default,,0,0,0,,而且百鬼丸大哥哥他…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.14,0:07:09.20,Default,,0,0,0,,媽媽？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.14,0:07:11.81,Default,,0,0,0,,說我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.53,0:07:18.51,Default,,0,0,0,,我是多羅羅啊 媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.48,0:07:21.33,Default,,0,0,0,,多羅羅？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.47,0:07:31.42,Default,,0,0,0,,大哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.26,0:07:34.05,Default,,0,0,0,,別拽了好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.05,0:07:36.02,Default,,0,0,0,,大哥哥 看看這個人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.06,0:07:47.04,Default,,0,0,0,,是妖怪嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.42,0:07:48.03,Default,,0,0,0,,不是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.22,0:07:50.27,Default,,0,0,0,,是人啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.65,0:07:51.48,Default,,0,0,0,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.00,0:07:55.27,Default,,0,0,0,,我叫阿鰹
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.77,0:07:56.75,Default,,0,0,0,,阿鰹？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.96,0:07:59.40,Default,,0,0,0,,然後 這裡是我家
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.56,0:08:08.54,Default,,0,0,0,,阿鰹一個人住嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.97,0:08:09.91,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.23,0:08:14.29,Default,,0,0,0,,偶爾有路人來瀑布會留下食物
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.29,0:08:15.41,Default,,0,0,0,,我就靠這些為生
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.82,0:08:17.52,Default,,0,0,0,,剛剛那個瀑布啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.28,0:08:21.00,Default,,0,0,0,,說起來為什麼那座佛像沒有臉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.22,0:08:26.51,Default,,0,0,0,,那是很久以前的事了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.85,0:08:31.27,Default,,0,0,0,,以前有位武士來到瀑布前
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.52,0:08:35.99,Default,,0,0,0,,發現了被沖刷成不動尊形狀的岩石
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.72,0:08:38.27,Default,,0,0,0,,本來那位武士
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.53,0:08:41.95,Default,,0,0,0,,就因為雕刻的佛像面容安詳而聞名
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.25,0:08:44.90,Default,,0,0,0,,但是到了武士時代
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.09,0:08:48.21,Default,,0,0,0,,人們開始敬仰威風滿面的不動尊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.49,0:08:51.15,Default,,0,0,0,,於是這位武士逐漸被人遺忘了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.60,0:08:53.35,Default,,0,0,0,,武士想要再次得到大家的青睞
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.66,0:08:55.97,Default,,0,0,0,,開始在岩石上雕刻不動尊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.44,0:08:58.71,Default,,0,0,0,,身體 手 腳
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.05,0:09:00.65,Default,,0,0,0,,到最後雕刻臉的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.83,0:09:02.14,Default,,0,0,0,,武士下定決心
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.73,0:09:06.68,Default,,0,0,0,,要雕刻出前所未有最威風的不動尊臉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.26,0:09:07.94,Default,,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.48,0:09:13.49,Default,,0,0,0,,雕刻出的臉全都似曾相識
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.08,0:09:18.45,Default,,0,0,0,,雕刻完又毀掉 長年累月周而復始
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.85,0:09:20.83,Default,,0,0,0,,武士慢慢變老
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.14,0:09:26.04,Default,,0,0,0,,最終也沒能完成 抱憾而終
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.34,0:09:29.82,Default,,0,0,0,,這故事聽不太懂啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.36,0:09:33.02,Default,,0,0,0,,對多羅羅來說還太早了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.14,0:09:34.42,Default,,0,0,0,,哇看起來真好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.98,0:09:36.14,Default,,0,0,0,,來 請慢用
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.83,0:09:38.11,Default,,0,0,0,,我開動了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.90,0:09:43.67,Default,,0,0,0,,多羅羅？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.46,0:09:47.55,Default,,0,0,0,,看到這粥我想起了媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.00,0:09:51.36,Default,,0,0,0,,說起來你把我叫做媽媽了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.98,0:09:52.50,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.94,0:09:54.65,Default,,0,0,0,,我長得特別像嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.52,0:09:57.27,Default,,0,0,0,,簡直一模一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.69,0:10:00.18,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼看都是我的媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.37,0:10:01.40,Default,,0,0,0,,連聲音都…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.60,0:10:03.34,Default,,0,0,0,,糟了…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.00,0:10:06.97,Default,,0,0,0,,哎呀 睡著了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.21,0:10:10.00,Default,,0,0,0,,畢竟最近都沒好好睡覺
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.67,0:10:12.30,Default,,0,0,0,,不要吵醒他好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.47,0:10:22.28,Default,,0,0,0,,這裡晚上很冷
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.34,0:10:35.05,Default,,0,0,0,,可惡 第一次吃到這麼好吃的飯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.94,0:10:43.35,Default,,0,0,0,,是嗎 太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.78,0:10:44.94,Default,,0,0,0,,多謝款待
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.80,0:10:49.05,Default,,0,0,0,,請問…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.81,0:10:50.51,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.25,0:10:54.26,Default,,0,0,0,,我…還是…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.23,0:11:01.74,Default,,0,0,0,,叫你媽媽可以嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.60,0:11:07.57,Default,,0,0,0,,比起阿鰹 還是媽媽更合適吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.01,0:11:11.76,Default,,0,0,0,,多羅羅真是愛撒嬌
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.76,0:11:14.86,Default,,0,0,0,,可以喔 你喜歡就好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.22,0:11:20.12,Default,,0,0,0,,媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.53,0:11:22.44,Default,,0,0,0,,我在喔
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.29,0:11:34.09,Default,,0,0,0,,安心下來之後我好像也睏了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.10,0:11:38.80,Default,,0,0,0,,是嗎 我還擔心藥不起作用
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.30,0:11:41.84,Default,,0,0,0,,什麼東西？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.33,0:11:44.80,Default,,0,0,0,,剛剛那位武士的故事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.16,0:11:46.81,Default,,0,0,0,,還有後續喔
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.57,0:11:51.01,Default,,0,0,0,,那位武士死後
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.42,0:11:56.27,Default,,0,0,0,,不動尊不知何時被妖怪依附了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.77,0:11:59.02,Default,,0,0,0,,為了完成武士的遺願
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.04,0:12:02.43,Default,,0,0,0,,想要一張臉 想要一張臉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.39,0:12:05.50,Default,,0,0,0,,不動尊復活了武士
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.86,0:12:08.65,Default,,0,0,0,,命令她把活人帶過去
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.06,0:12:11.87,Default,,0,0,0,,為了把人臉獻給不動尊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.97,0:12:15.88,Default,,0,0,0,,我就是那位武士
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.50,0:12:19.33,Default,,0,0,0,,通過不動尊的力量讀取對方的想法
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.66,0:12:22.47,Default,,0,0,0,,就能隨意改變自己的相貌與聲音
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.46,0:12:26.09,Default,,0,0,0,,孩子的臉不適合不動尊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.57,0:12:29.29,Default,,0,0,0,,但如果是那個男人的臉…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.06,0:12:58.79,Default,,0,0,0,,多羅羅
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.88,0:13:00.68,Default,,0,0,0,,多羅羅
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.47,0:13:02.36,Default,,0,0,0,,媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.65,0:13:05.18,Default,,0,0,0,,多羅羅真是愛撒嬌
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.33,0:13:06.27,Default,,0,0,0,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.44,0:13:10.85,Default,,0,0,0,,那就把這張臉獻給不動尊吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.38,0:13:16.28,Default,,0,0,0,,大哥哥？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.23,0:13:23.08,Default,,0,0,0,,等著我 大哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.19,0:13:25.13,Default,,0,0,0,,我這就去救你
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.54,0:13:36.25,Default,,0,0,0,,大哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.79,0:13:40.97,Default,,0,0,0,,大哥哥！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.56,0:13:44.34,Default,,0,0,0,,多羅羅！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.70,0:13:47.55,Default,,0,0,0,,你為什麼要來
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.79,0:13:48.53,Default,,0,0,0,,媽媽！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.41,0:13:51.50,Default,,0,0,0,,把大哥哥還給我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.36,0:13:57.57,Default,,0,0,0,,我都沒有捆住你
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.77,0:13:59.11,Default,,0,0,0,,為什麼不逃跑
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.67,0:14:01.44,Default,,0,0,0,,你這混蛋…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.44,0:14:01.95,Default,,0,0,0,,住手！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.15,0:14:09.82,Default,,0,0,0,,我絕對不會把大哥哥交給你
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.60,0:14:13.17,Default,,0,0,0,,你放開
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.34,0:14:14.34,Default,,0,0,0,,絕對不放
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.78,0:14:18.10,Default,,0,0,0,,我發誓要跟隨大哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.51,0:14:19.61,Default,,0,0,0,,這傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.39,0:14:24.07,Default,,0,0,0,,多羅羅
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.30,0:14:28.49,Default,,0,0,0,,睡得真香啊 大哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.14,0:15:41.12,Default,,0,0,0,,住手吧 百鬼丸
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.89,0:15:43.15,Default,,0,0,0,,已經夠了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.53,0:15:45.70,Default,,0,0,0,,沒有必要毀掉它了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.28,0:15:48.22,Default,,0,0,0,,那個聲音 是大哥哥的…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.51,0:15:51.10,Default,,0,0,0,,好了 來媽媽身邊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.25,0:15:52.01,Default,,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.49,0:15:56.45,Default,,0,0,0,,你是阿鰹
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.86,0:16:01.39,Default,,0,0,0,,為什麼…為什麼我的臉沒有變？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.86,0:16:04.91,Default,,0,0,0,,你不知道自己母親的相貌嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.06,0:16:13.96,Default,,0,0,0,,臉…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.69,0:16:16.31,Default,,0,0,0,,把臉給我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.68,0:16:17.35,Default,,0,0,0,,一直…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.15,0:16:21.06,Default,,0,0,0,,我一直都在尋找這張臉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.51,0:16:24.23,Default,,0,0,0,,好了 不要這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.33,0:16:25.06,Default,,0,0,0,,媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.40,0:16:26.24,Default,,0,0,0,,閉嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.52,0:16:29.09,Default,,0,0,0,,我想要他的臉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.48,0:16:31.93,Default,,0,0,0,,至今為止找到的最好的臉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.93,0:16:34.68,Default,,0,0,0,,為什麼非要這麼好的臉呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.46,0:16:36.97,Default,,0,0,0,,有眼睛 有牙齒
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.08,0:16:38.84,Default,,0,0,0,,還有嘴巴 這已經足夠了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.48,0:16:41.55,Default,,0,0,0,,但是阿鰹卻肆意妄為
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.17,0:16:45.44,Default,,0,0,0,,變成了一個欺騙別人 掠奪人臉的妖怪
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.49,0:16:47.46,Default,,0,0,0,,妖怪…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.91,0:16:48.66,Default,,0,0,0,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.55,0:16:51.38,Default,,0,0,0,,為什麼要這麼做
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.73,0:16:56.61,Default,,0,0,0,,你考慮一下被扒下臉的人的感受啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.85,0:17:02.67,Default,,0,0,0,,難受 不甘 傷心
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.78,0:17:14.93,Default,,0,0,0,,最好的臉…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.66,0:17:17.80,Default,,0,0,0,,比所有的不動尊都好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.91,0:17:20.44,Default,,0,0,0,,為什麼 為什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.91,0:17:21.71,Default,,0,0,0,,我不明白
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.08,0:17:24.72,Default,,0,0,0,,從何時開始 從何時開始…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.90,0:17:29.20,Default,,0,0,0,,從何時開始 我變成了這樣…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.90,0:17:32.56,Default,,0,0,0,,不行了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.06,0:17:37.96,Default,,0,0,0,,我已經不行了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.57,0:18:14.41,Default,,0,0,0,,多羅羅
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.08,0:18:19.61,Default,,0,0,0,,放在你的臉上…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.61,0:18:26.06,Default,,0,0,0,,對我笑一笑
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.57,0:18:34.94,Default,,0,0,0,,真是個溫柔的孩子 多羅羅
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.78,0:18:38.71,Default,,0,0,0,,你的笑臉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.80,0:18:44.90,Default,,0,0,0,,就像佛陀一樣…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.32,0:19:03.33,Default,,0,0,0,,媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.36,0:19:22.84,Default,,0,0,0,,大哥哥 對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.13,0:19:25.60,Default,,0,0,0,,我本想自己先振作起來
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.88,0:19:27.93,Default,,0,0,0,,卻增加了你的負擔
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.93,0:19:29.49,Default,,0,0,0,,還讓你想起了母親
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.75,0:19:33.64,Default,,0,0,0,,雖然大哥哥一直在幫助我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.23,0:19:36.28,Default,,0,0,0,,不過你遇到困難的話 我絕對…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.20,0:19:38.75,Default,,0,0,0,,好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.78,0:19:41.48,Default,,0,0,0,,我又搞砸了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.79,0:19:42.41,Default,,0,0,0,,多羅羅
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.95,0:19:46.06,Default,,0,0,0,,我沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.25,0:19:48.93,Default,,0,0,0,,溫泉 去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.42,0:19:54.36,Default,,0,0,0,,等一下 等等我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.60,0:19:57.97,Default,,0,0,0,,那…那個
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.36,0:20:01.05,Default,,0,0,0,,溫泉附近有妖怪出現
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.26,0:20:03.19,Default,,0,0,0,,其實是騙你的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.43,0:20:05.74,Default,,0,0,0,,當時…怎麼說呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.74,0:20:06.25,Default,,0,0,0,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.61,0:20:15.22,Default,,0,0,0,,大哥哥 這裡這裡！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.04,0:20:19.22,Default,,0,0,0,,太棒了 我還是第一次泡溫泉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.80,0:20:23.89,Default,,0,0,0,,不要看喔 大哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.34,0:20:26.29,Default,,0,0,0,,雖然知道你看不見
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.00,0:20:29.89,Default,,0,0,0,,所以說 不要看啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.43,0:20:33.48,Default,,0,0,0,,好痛…滲進傷口了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.14,0:20:36.33,Default,,0,0,0,,但是好舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.96,0:20:40.30,Default,,0,0,0,,這就是所謂極樂吧 大哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.30,0:20:40.86,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.55,0:20:44.00,Default,,0,0,0,,可能是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.28,0:20:48.95,Default,,0,0,0,,那麼就此死去也值了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.25,0:20:52.51,Default,,0,0,0,,妖怪
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.45,0:20:56.72,Default,,0,0,0,,和尚？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.96,0:20:58.30,Default,,0,0,0,,你從哪裡出來的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.24,0:21:01.87,Default,,0,0,0,,聽你這語氣真是過分啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.90,0:21:05.52,Default,,0,0,0,,在你們來之前就在啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.64,0:21:08.59,Default,,0,0,0,,真是的 這就是孽緣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.91,0:21:10.99,Default,,0,0,0,,哇 洗澡了 洗澡了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.13,0:21:12.48,Default,,0,0,0,,洗澡了！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.75,0:21:13.20,Default,,0,0,0,,我跳
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.77,0:21:17.70,Default,,0,0,0,,喂喂
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.40,0:21:22.08,Default,,0,0,0,,你們幹什麼 混蛋！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.27,0:21:24.51,Default,,0,0,0,,哎呀 真是抱歉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.51,0:21:26.53,Default,,0,0,0,,他們一直都很淘氣
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.67,0:21:28.09,Default,,0,0,0,,原諒他們吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.27,0:21:29.80,Default,,0,0,0,,你從哪裡來的？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.94,0:21:30.70,Default,,0,0,0,,哪裡？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.28,0:21:33.00,Default,,0,0,0,,這附近沒見過你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.09,0:21:33.99,Default,,0,0,0,,沒見過呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.82,0:21:36.87,Default,,0,0,0,,我們一直在旅行
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.07,0:21:39.51,Default,,0,0,0,,旅行？ 要去哪裡？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.32,0:21:41.82,Default,,0,0,0,,是要去哪個地方嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.03,0:21:45.57,Default,,0,0,0,,這個…我還沒想好
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.71,0:21:48.44,Default,,0,0,0,,那個人是你的哥哥嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.62,0:21:50.17,Default,,0,0,0,,大哥哥就是大哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.91,0:21:52.65,Default,,0,0,0,,這是什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.15,0:21:55.75,Default,,0,0,0,,你的背上好像寫了什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.33,0:21:59.92,Default,,0,0,0,,你…你幹什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.18,0:22:01.39,Default,,0,0,0,,不要老盯著看
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.39,0:22:03.91,Default,,0,0,0,,這是地圖吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.91,0:22:04.57,Default,,0,0,0,,地圖？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.80,0:22:06.52,Default,,0,0,0,,地圖 是地圖！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.52,0:22:07.49,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 就是
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.49,0:22:09.07,Default,,0,0,0,,這絕對是地圖
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.22,0:22:10.42,Default,,0,0,0,,地圖
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.42,0:22:11.76,Default,,0,0,0,,再給我看看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.76,0:22:12.66,Default,,0,0,0,,吵死了！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.01,0:22:15.38,Default,,0,0,0,,不要老盯著人家身體看！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.60,0:22:18.14,Default,,0,0,0,,沒關係吧 讓我們看看嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.02,0:22:19.87,Default,,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.36,0:22:22.57,Default,,0,0,0,,看到了 看到了…
